{"type":null,"faqId":47408,"title":"如何提高游戏流畅性？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{color:#333333;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">点击“手机管家”&gt;“加速优化”＞“一键结束”，结束暂时不使用的应用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">点击“手机管家”&gt;“空间清理”，根据屏幕提示清理手机中的垃圾。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">点击“设置”&gt;“开机自动启动”，禁止不需要开机启动的应用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">重启手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">此外，游戏画面与手机屏幕尺寸不一致，在运行时需要进行相关兼容性适配处理；游戏中加入了大量特效或需要调用特殊的传感器处理，都会影响游戏流畅性。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">若以上方法均不能解决问题，建议备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2992","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219314000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":88,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"提高,游戏速度","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}